---
layout: layouts/page-simple.njk
title: "Remodeling Blog"
meta_description: "Practical remodeling advice for Bozeman homeowners — bathroom costs, basement finishing, deck building, and what to expect when you remodel."
h1: "The Heartwood Blog"
permalink: "/blog/"
---

<p>Practical advice for Bozeman homeowners planning a remodel. Real numbers, real process, no fluff.</p>

<div class="blog-grid">
{% for post in collections.blog %}
  <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="card blog-card">
    {% if post.data.featured_image %}
    <img src="{{ post.data.featured_image }}" alt="{{ post.data.title }}" loading="lazy">
    {% endif %}
    <div class="blog-card-body">
      <h3>{{ post.data.title }}</h3>
      <p class="blog-card-meta">{{ post.date | dateReadable }}</p>
    </div>
  </a>
{% endfor %}
</div>
